
INTRODUCTION
    OSScroll is scroller using graphics.library/ScrollVPort routine
    synchronized by copper to achieve smoothest scrolling even on
    plain A1200 with lots of free CPU time.

    ___ALL ON INTUITION SCREEN,  YOU CAN DRAG IT BY MOUSE !!!!___

USAGE
    Roll the screen using JoyStick,  break it via sending CTRL-C
    to the program.

REQUIREMENTS
    Requires KS3.0, asl V38, lowlevel.library V40 and ss.library
    (included) to run.  B'coz of 256col, you need AGA or better.

LEGAL
