    somewhere in the DOCs.

INFO ABOUT SOURCECODE
    All the code is OS-StyleGuide compliant.  Written using Genam.
    The code is in quickly coded assembler,  almost not commented,
    but using offset names and constants :^Q.
    Don't be affraid to send me queries.
    This has been tested with Enforcer and MungWall without problems.

